atlas.entity.view

Class PageView

  • java.lang.Object
    • atlas.entity.view.PageView

  • public class PageView
extends Object
    Represents a localized view of a page. Basically a set of attributes of PageContent and its related Page. Namely, attributes useful for generating page lists and links (ID, localized name, latin name, if page is published). Actual page content other than name is not included!
    Author:
    Michal Smrha
    See Also:
    Page, PageContent
